\caption{Phase diagram of SrCu$_2$(BO$_3$)$_2$ as a function of pressure $p$ and magnetic field $H$ obtained from the effective pinwheel model~$\mathcal{H}_{\rm pw}$.}
\label{pic:pd_pressure}
